column5: Home again:  where we belong g team work    being here   starting the season with one of these  and laughing together as we finish the day - 8 punch buggies (4 each) and a coho  we found a few spots where the water was 39 - 40. By next week, with the grace of some warm weather, things should be starting soon.
nice  I want to bring mine home this weekend too
Bad combo: G getting bigger and the fish getting smaller.  I hope to get out for some crappie in another week or two.
